quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,77,Na ha ba hlokomele hore Allah U tseba seo ba se patileng le seo ba se pepesang
  2,78,"Har’a bona ho teng batho ba sa tsebeng Lengolo ho hang hae se hona ho le utloela, ba mpa ba hakanya"
  2,79,"Kahoo ho malimabe ba ngotseng Lengolo ka matsoho a bona, ebe ba re: “lena le etsoa ho Allah,” e le hore ka lona ba tle ba ithekisetse ka thekoana e eisehang. Bomalimabe bo sallane le bona ka seo matsoho a bona a se ngotseng, etsoe bo sallane le batla fumana kuno ka lona"
  2,80,"Ebile ba re: “mollo o ke ke oa re thetsa haese matsatsi a `maloa feela.” E re: “na le amohetse ts’episo e tsoang ho Allah, – hobane Ruri Allah a ke ke a roba ts’episo ea hae – kapa e be le buoa seo le sa se tsebeng khahlanong le Allah?”"
  2,81,"Empa e mong le e mong ea entseng sebe, sebe sa hae se mo etselitse lesakana-la-nkope; ke balekane ba mollo; ba tla phela kamoo"
  2,82,"Haele ba kholoang ba bile ba etsa ka ho loka: ke balekane ba Serapa. Etsoe har’a sona ba tla phela ka hosafeleng"
  2,83,"Hopolang re entse selekane le bana ba Israele; se khumameleng mong kantle ho Allah, le hlomphe batsoali, le beng ka lona, le likhutsana, le bafumanehi, le buise batho ka hlonepho; le tsitlallele thapelong, le hona ho fana ka linyehelo.” empa kamor’a mona, eaba le ea koeneha tlas’a likhothaletso haese ba fokolang feela ba lona"